OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Stacey Foster
OL,7,Fspoke to Ofsted's new boss, Sir Martyn
OL,8,FOliver, about the findings from
OL,9,Feducation watchdogs independent review
OL,11,FThe head of Osted has said
OL,12,Facknowledged it "should be held
OL,13,Faccountable" after an independent
OL,14,Freview concluded that it's initial
OL,15,Fresponse to the death of headteacher
OL,16,FRuth Perry appeared "defensive and
OL,17,Fcomplacent".
