OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FMrs Perry took her life in January
OL,7,F2023 after an Ofsted report downgraded
OL,8,Fher Primary School in Reading from its
OL,9,Fhighest rating of "outstanding" to its
OL,10,Flowest rating ` "inadequate".
OL,12,FSir Martyn Oliver was appointed Chief
OL,13,FInspector of the watchdog a year later
OL,14,Fin January 2024 and today told ITV
OL,15,FNews he is "determined to make a
OL,16,Fdifference" with he findings from this
OL,17,Freport.
