OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FSir Oliver acknowledged that Ofsted is
OL,7,Fa "public body and we should be held
OL,8,Faccountable by the public and not be
OL,9,Fdefensive, but be open and transparent.
OL,11,F"I've always known that providers on
OL,12,Fthe whole didn't like the single word
OL,13,Fjudgement, but I genuinely thought
OL,14,Fthat parents and carers wanted that
OL,15,Fclarity and simplicity. But we've
OL,16,Fheard in the Big Listen that that's
OL,17,Fnot the case.
OL,19,F"Parents have said they want nuance"
OL,20,Fsaid Sir Oliver.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
