OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FChristine Gilbert, who led the report,
OL,7,Ffound that Ofsted did not make any
OL,8,Fattempt to contact the school in the
OL,9,Faftermath of Ruth's death.
OL,11,FWhen asked by ITV News why Ofsted did
OL,12,Fnot reach out to the school or family
OL,13,Fon a personal level, Sir Oliver
OL,14,Fresponded "That was before my time.
OL,16,F"On my second day I met Professor
OL,17,FWaters, who's been incredibly
OL,18,Fcourageous".
