OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FThe single word judgement framework
OL,7,Fthat Ofsted inspects against will
OL,8,Fremain in place over the next 12
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FAn overall effectiveness grade is
OL,12,Fformed from four sub-catagories:
OL,13,Fquality of education, behaviour and
OL,14,Fattitudes, personal development and
OL,15,Fleadership and management.
OL,17,FHowever, Sir Oliver states he "fully
OL,18,Faccepts" Dane Christine Gilbert's
OL,19,Frecommendations laid out in the report.
