OL,3,C'We should be held accountable':
OL,4,COfsted's boss on independent report
OL,6,FSince taking over as Chief Inspector
OL,7,FSir Oliver argues he has introduced
OL,8,F"significant change" to the way Ofsted
OL,9,Foperates:
OL,11,F"People can feel a difference on the
OL,12,Fground and along with the Secretary of
OL,13,FState, we are resetting relationships,
OL,14,Fworking together and working
OL,15,Ftransparently with the trade unions,
OL,16,Fwith people, making sure that we build
OL,17,Fa better accountability system going
OL,18,Fforward, but still champion children,
OL,19,Fespecially the most vulnerable, to
OL,20,Fhave the best education and care
OL,21,Fpossible."
